prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Virginia. Governor (1922-1926 : Trinkle). Executive Papers of Governor E. Lee Trinkle, 1919-1929 [bulk 1922-1926]. Accession 21567b, State government records collection, The Library of Virginia, Richmond, Virginia.

acqinfo.head: Acquisition Information
acqinfo.p: Transferred from the Office of the Secretary of the Commonwealth, 18 May 1939.

bioghist.head: Biographical Information
bioghist.p: Governor E. Lee Trinkle was born

scopecontent.head: Scope and Content
scopecontent.p: Governor E. Lee Trinkle Executive Papers, 1919-1929 [bulk 1922-1926], are organized into two series. Series have been designated for Subject Files and Extraditions and Pardons.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is arranged into the following series:

list.item: Series II. Extraditions, Pardons, and Prison Affairs, 1922-1926
